TITLE: Querying Multiple Feed Values in Wei - Solidity
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the bulk retrieval of multiple feed values in wei (18 decimal places) from FTSOv2 using getFeedsByIdInWei. The caller supplies an array of feed IDs and may pay a fee. Returns arrays of values in wei and a single timestamp. Ideal for high-precision requirements or systems standardized on wei-based values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/flare-foundation/developer-hub.git/blob/main/docs/ftso/solidity-reference/FtsoV2Interface.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
function getFeedsByIdInWei(
    bytes21[] _feedIds
) external payable returns (
    uint256[] _values,
    uint64 _timestamp
);
```

