TITLE: Submitting Attestation Request to FDC Protocol - Solidity Foundry
DESCRIPTION: Implements end-to-end submission of an ABI-encoded attestation request to the FDC smart contract, managing private key loading, contract lookups, broadcast sessions, request fee calculation, and payment. Uses the `ContractRegistry` library to find contract addresses and Foundry's VM methods for broadcasting. Requires contract interfaces (`IFdcRequestFeeConfigurations`, `IFdcHub`), a private key provisioned via `.env`, and previously encoded input data.
