TITLE: Retrieving FTSOv2 Feeds via web3.py - Python
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates use of web3.py to access the Flare FtsoV2 contract and read feed data for FLR/USD, BTC/USD, and ETH/USD. Requires installation of the web3 Python package, the FtsoV2 contract ABI, the RPC endpoint, and the appropriate feed IDs. The code outputs feed value and latest timestamp for each asset pair; ensure your ABI and network details match the targeted chain.
