TITLE: UTF8 Hex Encoding Functions
DESCRIPTION: Utility functions for converting strings to UTF8 hex format and padding them to 32 bytes, used in request preparation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/flare-foundation/developer-hub.git/blob/main/docs/fdc/guides/hardhat/evm-transaction.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
function toHex(data: string) {
  var result = "";
  for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
    result += data.charCodeAt(i).toString(16);
  }
  return result.padEnd(64, "0");
}
```

